EditorData.logicalname: DOESN'T KNOW MUSHROOM HUNTER IS MISSING

Text.Value: Mind's slipping... made him less of a bastard...
*The corpse does not stir. It will answer no more questions.*
Baelen's in danger. How do I help?
*The spell's power wanes. You can ask no more questions.*
Mushroom. Heals anything... Very rare. Very valuable...
*The corpse seems willing to speak - but not to its killer.*

Synopsis: Speak with Dead dialogue with Derryth Bonecloak, a dwarven alchemist from Baldur's Gate who came to the Underdark along with her husband, Baelen, in search of a rare and valuable mushroom - the noblestalk.
